All previously listed items are resolved by the 2026 modernization pass:

- [done] Feature parity with ScalaCheck-style combinators (boolean, numeric,
  string, array/list, set, map, tuple, record, object, date, option,
  suchThat, sized/resize, pick, shuffle) plus `forAll` / `exists`
  quantifiers with shrinking.
- [done] `[...Array(n)]` repetition replaced with the `range` / `repeatGenerator`
  helpers in `src/internal/range.ts`.
- [done] Convenience `sample()` / `sampleN()` on `Generator` removes the need
  to call `generate().get()`.
- [done] Documentation generated from source (TypeDoc + VitePress) and
  deployed to GitHub Pages via `.github/workflows/docs.yml`.
